casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Cheren, Appellant, v. Troutman, Sheriff, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Cheren v. Troutman (1994), 69 Ohio St.3d 692.]

(No. 94-131 Submitted June 15, 1994 Decided July 27, 1994.) Oles Cheren, pro se. Lynn C. Slaby, Summit County Prosecuting Attorney, and Jason T. Adams, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., AW. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
